 Our Firm

 


With thirty years of experience in the micro-cap space, not only does Perritt have a commitment to small companies—we operate as a small company.
Sharing a boots-to-the-ground mentality with the micro-cap companies we invest in, our commitment and knowledge of the micro-cap space is consistent across all of our investment strategies. Other firms may offer investments in micro-cap securities as part of a larger whole philosophy. We only invest in fundamentally and financially sound micro-cap companies and do not stray from this focus.
 


