 Some companies that are related to ITT include Spirit Aerosystems Holdings (SPR), Arrow Electronics (ARW), LATAM Airlines Group S.A. (LTM), RPM International (RPM), Spectrum Brands Holdings (SPB), 58.com (WUBA), Envision Healthcare Corporation (EVHC), CF Industries Holdings (CF), Pinnacle Foods (PF), Owens Corning (OC), W.P. Carey (WPC), PLDT (PHI), Westar Energy (WR), Macy's (M), Kilroy Realty Corporation (KRC), OGE Energy Corp. (OGE), Dr. Reddy's Laboratories Ltd (RDY) and Vipshop Holdings Limited (VIPS).



